  "content": "## What's Inside\n## Try These Searches\n\n## Fresh Ingest\n\nThe workspace ships with pre-ingested knowledge. To rebuild from scratch:\n\n```bash\ncorvia workspace ingest --fresh\n```\n```\n\n**Step 5: Initialize git repo**\n\n```bash\ncd /root/corvia-workspace && git init && git add -A && git commit -m \"init: corvia-workspace demo repo\"\n```\n\n**Step 6: Commit (this is a separate repo, already committed above)**\n\n---\n",
